        Creates a new decoded skin model
        Parameters:
        timestamp - when was the skin fetched from Mojang
        uuid - premium UUID of the Owner
        name - case-sensitive name of the owner
        skinHash - short skin url or empty
        skinModel - true if slim model otherwise false for steve
        capeHash - short cape url or empty
